WEBVTT

00:00.939 --> 00:02.239
<i>Before there was sex...</i>

00:02.273 --> 00:04.938
<i>before there was the city,</i>
<i>there was just me,</i>

00:05.058 --> 00:07.693
<i>Carrie... Carrie Bradshaw</i>
<i>from Castlebury, Connecticut.</i>

00:07.728 --> 00:08.861
Can I help you?

00:08.895 --> 00:10.129
Hi, sir.
I'm Dorrit's boyfriend.

00:10.163 --> 00:11.630
What the hell is going on?
If I didn't meet your dad,

00:11.665 --> 00:12.932
he'd never let you
out of the house again.

00:12.966 --> 00:15.367
That wasn't your call.
It was mine.

00:15.402 --> 00:16.869
You pretend to be above
the idea of commitment,

00:16.903 --> 00:19.472
but the truth is,
you're just afraid to connect.

00:19.506 --> 00:20.906
I'm not afraid of commitment.

00:20.941 --> 00:22.741
I'm sure the girls at
your school are all over you.

00:22.776 --> 00:24.243
Not the one that matters.

00:24.277 --> 00:25.611
How about you,
my budding literary lion?

00:25.645 --> 00:27.012
How's the pitch coming?

00:27.047 --> 00:28.781
Well, I think I've finally
narrowed it down to Adam Weaver.

00:28.815 --> 00:29.982
The young playwright
I've been reading about

00:30.016 --> 00:31.250
in Arts & Leisure?

00:31.284 --> 00:32.918
Some of us are headed
to McSorley's to grab a drink.

00:32.953 --> 00:35.387
You wanna come?
Yeah, I'd love to.

00:35.422 --> 00:37.656
You get me a juicy interview,
and I will publish it.

00:37.691 --> 00:40.192
- This is definitely off the record.
- Definitely.

00:40.312 --> 00:43.310
